overview: Bonus DVD for Rage's Strings To A Web album featuring footage from Wacken Open Air 2009, Masters Of Rock 2009 & Live in Sofia 2009  Wacken Open Air:  01: Carved In Stone  02: Higher Than The Sky  03: Set This World On Fire  04: All I Want  05: Invisible Horizons  06: Lord Of The Flies  07: From The Cradle To The Grave  08: Prayers Of Steel  09: Suicide  10: Down  11: Soundchaser  Masters Of Rock:  12: Set This World On Fire  13: All I Want  Live In Sofia:  14: Carved In Stone  15: Never Give Up
title: Rage: Official Festival Bootleg
